by its weight.  And that is cool to know about the 5 vs 3 <s>pin</s> <span style="color: #FF80BF">screw</span> part... both of my converter carts ha<s>ve</s><span style="color: #FF80BF">d</span> 5 <s>pins</s> <span style="color: #FF80BF">screws</span>. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><br /><span style="color: #FF80BF">edit.</span>

		

